msgstr "Примеры конфигурации"

msgid "Development (InMemory)"
msgstr "Разработка (InMemory)"

msgid "Production (SQLite)"
msgstr "Продакшн (SQLite)"

msgid "Production with DI (SQLite)"
msgstr "Продакшн с DI (SQLite)"

msgid "appsettings.json (SQLite)"
msgstr "appsettings.json (SQLite)"

msgid "Migration from Previous Versions"
msgstr "Миграция с предыдущих версий"

msgid "If you are upgrading from VibeMQ 1.2.x:"
msgstr "При обновлении с VibeMQ 1.2.x:"

msgid ""
"``IMessageStore`` is now deprecated. It still works but will be removed "
"in a future version. Migrate to ``IStorageProvider``."
msgstr ""
"``IMessageStore`` устарел. Он по-прежнему работает, но будет удалён в "
"будущей версии. Мигрируйте на ``IStorageProvider``."

msgid ""
"``InMemoryMessageStore`` is deprecated in favor of "
"``InMemoryStorageProvider``."
msgstr ""
"``InMemoryMessageStore`` устарел в пользу ``InMemoryStorageProvider``."

msgid ""
"No breaking changes — the default behavior (in-memory) is preserved. "
